# Q1 2026 Implementation Plan - AgentsFlowAI

**Target Completion Date:** March 31, 2026
**Planning Date:** December 27, 2025

---

## Executive Summary

After analyzing the current project state, I recommend a phased approach over Q1 2026 to build a fully-featured, production-ready application. This plan breaks down development into 5 manageable phases with clear milestones and deliverables.

---

## Current State Analysis

### ✅ What's Already Built

1. **Core Infrastructure**
   - Next.js 14+ application structure
   - Prisma ORM with PostgreSQL schema
   - Authentication infrastructure (NextAuth.js configured)
   - API routes for most features

2. **Navigation & Pages**
   - Dashboard layout with sidebar navigation
   - AI Agents management pages
   - AI Usage analytics
   - Dashboard stats API
   - Leads management
   - Services management
   - Appointments system
   - Chat functionality
   - Fast-chat page

3. **AI Integration**
   - Multi-model AI support with fallback chain
   - Ollama integration
   - Call handler for Twilio
   - AI agents configuration

4. **Integrations**
   - Crustdata integration
   - Forager integration
   - People Data Labs integration

### ❌ What's Missing / Incomplete

1. **Authentication**
   - User registration flow incomplete
   - Role-based access control not fully implemented
   - Session management needs testing

2. **Dashboard**
   - Dashboard stats API returns mock data
   - Charts and visualizations incomplete
   - Real-time updates not implemented

3. **AI Agents**
   - Agent creation/editing UI incomplete
   - Agent performance analytics missing
   - Workflow automation not built

4. **Lead Management**
   - Lead enrichment integration incomplete
   - Lead scoring not implemented
   - Bulk operations missing

5. **Appointments**
   - Calendar view incomplete
   - Reminder system missing
   - Booking flow needs polish

6. **Chat**
   - Real-time chat not implemented
   - Chat history incomplete
   - File attachments missing

7. **Testing & Polish**
   - Unit tests incomplete
   - E2E tests missing
   - Error handling needs improvement
   - Mobile responsiveness issues

---

## Phase 1: Authentication & Core Infrastructure

### Goals

- Complete user authentication system
- Implement role-based access control
- Set up proper session management
- Create user onboarding flow

### Deliverables

#### 1.1 Authentication System

- [ ] Complete user registration API
- [ ] Implement email verification
- [ ] Add password reset functionality
- [ ] Set up session management with NextAuth.js
- [ ] Add social login (Google, GitHub)

#### 1.2 Authorization

- [ ] Define user roles (Admin, User, Viewer)
- [ ] Implement role-based middleware
- [ ] Add permission checks to all API routes
- [ ] Create API key management for integrations

#### 1.3 User Management

- [ ] User profile pages
- [ ] Account settings
- [ ] Team management (optional)
- [ ] User activity logging

### Technical Tasks
```typescript
// src/app/api/auth/register/route.ts - Complete registration
// src/lib/auth.ts - Configure NextAuth.js
// src/middleware.ts - Add role-based protection
// prisma/schema.prisma - Add role fields
```

